dxf2svg.util.svglink
Class PartNumberLinks

java.lang.Object
  dxf2svg.util.svglink.PartNumberLinks
public class PartNumberLinks
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides context for an SVG search. In this case this class is completely customized to search for the ID of a wire if it ends in a hyperlink and place the name of the wire as the ID of the wire.

Field Detail

PART_INDEX_NO

public static final java.lang.String PART_INDEX_NO
The regex for determining part number and access panel numbers. For more details on how part numbers see EventAttributeModifier.stringAsIntPadChar(java.lang.String), but this regex effectively catches access panel numbers and part numbers but does not interfer with the handling of EventAttributeModifier.stringAsIntPadChar(java.lang.String)'s part number padding scheme.
